A pressure group under the auspices of South-South Atiku/Obi Support Base, on Wednesday, congratulated former Vice President of Nigeria, Atiku Abubakar on his emergence as the flag bearer of the Peopleâ€™s Democratic Party, PDP which held in Port-Harcourt Rivers State. In a statement by King Para Ekiyes and Barr. E.K. Ebis, Chairman and Publicity Secretary respectively, the group urged Nigerians to come out enmass to support Alahaji Atiku Abubakar during the coming Presidential elections. The Group stated that it is only a trusted and tested conbination like like Alhaji Atiku Abubakar and Mr. Peter Obi that can save the Country from poverty and insecurity. The group also called on the Independent National Electoral Commission, INEC to avoid being partisan to any candidate on political party. The group vowed to mobilize thousands of its followers and the South-South region to vote for the former Vice President and his running mate, Mr. Peter Obi which they described as the solution for a better Nigeria. Francis Sadhere, Warri 